verbose_text: Interestingly, deletion of Igfr in macrophages led to significant reduction in NLRP3 inflammasome dependent caspase-1 and IL-1beta activation induced by extracellular ATP, urate crystals, sodium arsenite, and ceramides (XREF_FIG).
evidence: Igfr in macrophages led to significant reduction in NLRP3 inflammasome-dependent caspase-1 and IL-1beta
